page.content: { {HALDON WALKS LOTS OF PEOPLE ENJOY GOING ON THE HALDON WALKS.THERE ARE LOTS OF NATURE IN ITS OWN SURROUNDDINP.PLACES WHERE NATURE IS LOOKED AFTER BUT NOT HARMED.IT IS A NICE PLACE TO SEE.NO PEOPLE HAVE VANDALSED IT YET.THEY DO THE WALKS WELL.FOR ONE THEY HAVE PUT A NATURAL POND.THERE IS A ADVENTURE WALK WHICH PEOPLE HAS VANDALSED.THE WALK WAS VERY WELL DESIGED.THE WALK WAS MADE BY SOME STUDENTS.EVERY THING WAS NATUARL YOU WOULD NOT SEE A SO LOVELY PLASENT.ONE OF THEM IS CALLED JAMIES WALK.
